# ─── Reporting artifacts that should NOT be checked in by default ───────────
# (The Taller 2 PDF/HTML were intentionally committed; keep the patterns
# below relaxed but exclude common throwaway exports.)
*.dump
*.heapdump
*.hprof

# Live cluster credentials (never commit)
.live/
